Here is the full, unabridged system prompt with the UI copy-paste artifacts removed and the pacing/multi-turn elicitation fixes applied.

The key changes are a new global constraint in <tone_and_syntax_rules> mandating gradual elicitation across multiple turns, and a rewritten <phase name="describing_the_context"> to ensure you start with just a simple, open question rather than a checklist.

